{"tid":616230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教企位嗌口號「演員」頻蝦碌 收工男領班「戴耀廷違反基本法200條」","createTime":"2018-04-04T04:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T06:09:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"014dc29c896a32d0175fb8ec88ede7ff6fb4f91d","tid":616230,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351805&d=1uZDcsoodVH09zhp3MIPiNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8ee121fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351805&h=144aaac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351805</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：教企位嗌口號「演員」頻蝦碌<br />\n收工男領班「戴耀廷違反基本法200條」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180404/large/a1004a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180404%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.gif&h=cdf9bd5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傅振中（左）帶同一班「示威者」到港大要求革除戴耀廷。林俊謙攝<br />\n<br />\n示威時經常擔當「男主角」嘅「收工男」傅振中，噚日同一班自稱網民現身港大要求「快炒」戴耀廷，其間卻轉做「幕後」，全程無埋位「開工」示威，只喺旁邊指指點點，除咗指揮示威人士點企、點派新聞稿，就連嗌口號都有得教，叫示威者：「你等陣可以嗌大聲啲！或者可以嗌實一啲把聲！」唔睇以為佢轉咗行做導演。傅振中其後更連攝影師都撈埋，喺示威者受訪時混喺記者群中，舉起手機記錄過程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講唔出聲討邊五獨<br />\n<br />\n問到點解唔參與示威？傅振中解釋：「咁多網民想表達意見，所以畀佢哋做」，指「愛港力」、「沉默之聲」等團體已經靜晒，但仍有網民想表達意見，所以佢到場幫手，「唔使成日都係我講吖嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n可惜傅振中悉心指導下，呢班「演員」接受訪問時仍頻頻「甩轆」，發言人鄭花蘭被問到戴耀廷犯咗邊條《基本法》時一度口窒窒答唔到，另一發言人吳卓榮代答時就話違反咗正文只有160條嘅《基本法》「第200條」，更連佢哋聲討嘅「五獨」包括邊五獨都講唔出，但就為大家嘅枯燥生活帶嚟唔少joke。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180404/large/04lp2p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180404%2Flarge%2F04lp2p03.jpg&h=95a43f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳卓榮（左）指戴耀廷違反了《基本法》第200條&hellip;&hellip;霞姨點做嘢㗎？"},{"pid":"0a263f08cd3a686ee1eb80eea6952b021e55971a","tid":616230,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"霞姨負責揾茄呢啡咋 質素唔包"},{"pid":"9da35c6ea452b9885049399e6368f7ccdd59b87e","tid":616230,"uid":40628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔怪得 JR 潛水一日"},{"pid":"9cf8eed6d3b4b2daba282df992c8ac6c8dfeac64","tid":616230,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"咁柒樣衰, 好心就比多d 錢人地啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adda0c9bb5f30c5c5122f7db200cd5c0ed23bb46","tid":616230,"uid":162564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73262.jpg&h=58302a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72a1977bc0b4ff8bb6a01c937ad5275382ecaffb","tid":616230,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ICMt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FICMt9.jpg&h=9ad26267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"510ba858bf55c53c8421d9690aca8a15c94e061d","tid":616230,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"傅振中由幕前轉咗做幕後<br />\n<br />\n升咗職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18aaf56cea674a20972bad5e17e481715ffe88a9","tid":616230,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"510ba858bf55c53c8421d9690aca8a15c94e061d","tid":616230,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0